        "Title": "Deployment Strategies in Kubernetes",
        "Description": "Building on the foundational knowledge, LU2 delves into practical aspects of application deployment, focusing on using Kubernetes primitives to implement common deployment strategies. This unit enhances learners' ability to align technical, functional, and service requirements within Kubernetes-based solution architectures, addressing the performance gap of solutions that do not meet stakeholder needs."
    },

