        "Title": "Monitoring and Debugging Kubernetes Applications",
        "Description": "LU3 escalates to a higher level of complexity where learners explore application observability and maintenance. This unit equips learners with skills to coordinate multiple Kubernetes solution components, ensuring compatibility and adherence to design framework goals, thus addressing the performance gap related to coordination challenges."
    },

