        "Title": "Security and Configuration Management in Kubernetes",
        "Description": "LU4 focuses on the importance of coding standards, scalability, and reusability in Kubernetes solutions. By understanding these principles, learners gain clarity on their significance, addressing the performance gap of unclear coding practices that can affect long-term application success."
